::Aerotaur::
       He stumbled through the brush towards the battle nearly colliding with 
Windlord.  "Ah, uh hello there."  He mumbles almost incoherently.  "Didn't 
mean to walk into you."  He shakes his head.  "Maybe you could tell me where 
I am, uh and who are you?"
